Now it's easier to PHP on Snap!

* You can now use the command `add-php-configuration` to add custom configuration ini files! Just add a command to your stage containing:
      add-php-configuration &lt;path to config ini file&gt;
* And for enabling extensions we now provide the command `enable-php-extension`. Add it to your stage:
      enable-php-extension &lt;extension name&gt;
* In addition to these changes we also added support for the version 5.6!
* Check our [docs](http://docs.snap-ci.com/the_ci_environment/languages/#php) for more info.
